t components in the bazaar and would strongly suggest anyone in need of research components give the bazaar a try.  If you go to Katta along the route from the Fungoid Zone, the Fungoid Grove ports to a building in the Twilight Sea zone.  In that building was a merchant who had Ice of Velious for water pet and jade shard for fire pet (if only I had known at the time).  Ice of velious can also be bought in the gnome pirate igloos off the iceclad docks (they are good aligned pirates) and in Thurgadin.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utangting.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TangTing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#333333>(9/13/02 8:52:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1505.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Research</span><hr size=1> Muppan,<br>
